<item>
            <title>[DATAREST-47] POST fails, when links : null</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-47</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since the last update fixing the update problem with links, there is a new error. Doing a POST with empty links results in a:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;org.springframework.http.converter.HttpMessageNotReadableException: Property &apos;links&apos; is not of array type. Either eliminate this property from the document or make it an array.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adding the links like this: &lt;br/&gt;
entity.setLinks(new ArrayList&amp;lt;LinkType&amp;gt;());&lt;br/&gt;
and it works, without any issues. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From my point of view it should also work with Links : null.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
